{"tid":2035563,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［527］極少數人？乜鳩撚屎叫極少數人呀？","createTime":"2020-05-26T04:08:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-26T08:03:13.000Z","uid":75796,"like":6,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"ac9dbfcc3017ea1afcdefd3ee56801e2d066b494","tid":2035563,"uid":75796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T04:08:38.000Z","msg":"港共政府同對家一直講緊港版國安法只係針對（所謂）<strong>極少數泛民同黑暴分子</strong>，你冇搞事唔會罰你㗎。<br />\n<br />\n但你同我同單眼佬都知香港黃絲係佔大多數<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，絕非極少數，所以到時所有黃絲都會俾人當係黑暴。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">無論你係勇定和，佢都可以屈你。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n所以佢點解要用極少數呢個字眼？<br />\n因為佢地想分化黃營囉<br />\n而家話你知只會拉極少數 慢慢黃絲手足就會縮 縮下縮下就會真係變咗極少數囉<br />\n然後個個都會好似支那人咁唔敢發聲 <br />\n發聲嘅個個都要做假膠 冒俾人拉嘅風險 <br />\n加上手足之間會難以聯繫 咁就會好難組織 <br />\n然後俾狗逐個捉 <strong>就會變成真點極少數</strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">得番極少數人 到時仲點攬炒？</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">但係<br />\n我地知道而家我地絕非極少數<br />\n所以手足們 <br />\n請用盡所有能力上做到嘅事<br />\n能力外嘅事都要盡力去做</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">527罷個工岀嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n打公仔？ 請日假囉（好快啲請喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n驚俾人秋後？呢啲公司做唔做都罷啦<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beg_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n網上戰呢 <br />\ntwitter任務做咗未呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nshare文宣俾老母 同事 鄰居 做未呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好基本㗎咋</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">我地已經豁咗岀去好耐啦</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n猶豫緊嘅你 唔該今日去睇下重溫下《十年》<br />\n自己睇又好 同另一半睇又好 同我睇都好（歡迎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">喺寄望其他國家嘅人幫我地之前 做好自己本分啦</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n一齊話俾對家知 唔係極少數人抗爭緊 係絕多數人 都對呢個政府不信任 而我地大多數人係絕對支持勇和兩家做嘅嘢 一開始已經講緊啦 <br />\n兄弟爬山各自努力 <br />\n<br />\n我地絕不會被分化<br />\n<br />\n民族自強 香港獨立<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/D3N8TPV.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FD3N8TPV.gif&h=c4d59f29&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1a05e96eee649e377583a646b3981164dbf65bb0","tid":2035563,"uid":262389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T04:10:51.000Z","msg":"關於沈教授20點之我見<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2035226\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2035226</a>"},{"pid":"e9a449c8934d83062e739e9478eb2eda4a38fe00","tid":2035563,"uid":37525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T05:01:16.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n但係罷一日工真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n工運唔係射波請一日假<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但之前肺炎無生意 又咁多手足失業<br />\n而家會罷一日都真係算畀面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b24804d37ff4f21ba9a626508fa258307c9205bf","tid":2035563,"uid":3357,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T08:03:13.000Z","msg":"黎明行動 金鐘相見<br />\n全民駕駛 以車代鐵<br />\n路面要車 地面要人<br />\n527塞爆港島<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}